# Carve in MkDocs

Welcome to the *mkdocs-carve* example site. This homepage is written in
/Carve/ and rendered straight into the MkDocs theme.

- Carve supports lists
- And `inline code`
- And [links](https://github.com/markup-carve)

| feature | works |
|---------|-------|
| tables  | yes   |
| bold    | yes   |
